          processes over 10,000 requests and payment transactions daily.
        </li>
        <li>
          Worked on the REST API for Complaint Management and Bureau Services
          (CMAB) tickets management system.
        </li>
        <li>
          Developed a USSD application for StarMicro Insurance and SanLam
