        </li>
        <li>
          Developed a web dashboard for the MTN Business Manager mobile app.
        </li>
        <li>
          Developed REST APIs for MTN Business Manager mobile application.
        </li>
      </ul>
    </TimeLineElement>

    <TimeLineElement
